es (2019-2021). Dr. Vuong has published more than 120 academic articles, and book chapters in about 50 refereed journals and books by such publishers as Elsevier, Inderscience, Nature Publishing Group, Springer, Praeger, Wiley, World Scientific, etc. Trung Tran is an Associate Professor of Mathematics Education and works at Vietnam Academy for Ethnic Minorities. He is a member of the Vietnam chapter of The European Association of Science Editors (EASE), a leader of the Vietnamese Science Editors (VSE) Team, and a chairman of Editor’s Board of Journal of Ethnic Minorities Research (ISSN: 0866-773X).  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Sep 2021) 0aHumanitieszVietnam. 0aSocial scienceszVietnam. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh1 aDoan, Xuan-Hung, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHo, Manh-Toan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHo, Manh-Tung, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHoang, Khanh-Linh, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHoang, Phuong-Hanh, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLa, Viet-Phuong, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLe, Thu-Hien T., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNguyen, Hong Kong T., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNguyen, Hong-Kong T., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNguyen, Minh-Hoang, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNguyen, Phuong-Tram T., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNguyen, Thu-Hang T., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNguyen, Tien-Trung, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/rel